  MainNeeds
  Need a wordpress Plugin which is able to upload woocommerce feautured and gallery images to ChatGPT and get a response, the response should be a json or array which is containing some SEO optimized text and the image titles, also the image IDs to help us update the images to improve our seo.
  Also need an status page to display the work progress and the results.
  keep in mind that we need to update the images and the alt/description text of images, so we need to update the old data with the new data which is coming from the ChatGPT response.
  Include current product title/description helping chatGPT to write a good seo optimized text.
  The Plugin should be able to run on a schedule and update the images and the text.
